Every day we interact with different type of energy in our day to day life, sometime we get some energy and some time we lose some energy.
If this interaction happen on the surface of mind then since on surface of mind we always feel lack of energy and due to lack of energy we unable to interact with internal part of nature.

***Lack of energy keep us engaged with objects***

Whatever we realize from our senses/mind that are the external arrangement of nature and there are many base/chaining of states inside object that keep the object what it seems to be us.

If the state of mind get transformed int to observation even somewhat you may precept the object in different ways. Every one have little of more power of observation and even we observe many things in our day to day life but because our states of energy range exists in very thin range we cant't observe beyond our state of energy.

But  if our states of energy get increased then we can realize not only the internal structures of object but also the energy flow inside that object.
We can realize the point of transformation in object.

If our state of energy get increased more and more then after certain period of time we can realize the different types of frequencies in nature.
Interaction with nature means not to talk with nature but we can observe how waves of different frequencies perceiving in nature.

***Every one interact with nature using there co state***

When our observation are capable to detect the frequency then only we can play with waves, there are many waves entering/emerging into/from us that affect our day to day life.
If we capable to detect these waves then no need to force to emerge/enter in to us but it automatically get truncated.

Because of non awareness only the high frequency energy having different state enter in to us and it influence/change the direction of thinking/feeling.
If we have awareness then the same energy get in use for us or at least it not influence our life.

***We are always in some state that can interact with nature only difference is that we interact in different ways based on states of energy within  us***

